[{"type":"{{","value":[["pagebanner"],["Mena-asia_default_banner.jpg"]]},"\n",{"type":"'''","value":["Hidaka"]}," (日高町) is a town in ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Hidaka (subprefecture)"],["Hidaka Subprefecture"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Hokkaido"]]},".\n\nThis article also covers ",{"type":"'''","value":["Biratori"]}," town.(平取町)\n\n",{"type":"==","value":[" Understand "]},"\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["File:Hidaka in Hidaka Subprefecture.gif"],["thumb"],["300px"],["Hidaka ward (north) and Monbetsu ward (south), with Biratori town in between the two."]]},"\nOn 2006, the town of Monbetsu was merged into the old Hidaka, giving rise to the current Hidaka town. The town's area is divided into two: Hidaka ward in the north and Monbetsu ward in the south. The town of Biratori left the merger talks and remained a separate town.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get in"]},"\n",{"type":"===","value":[" By train "]},"\nJR Hidaka main line runs in Monbetsu ward from ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Tomakomai"]]}," to ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Samani"]]},". Only local trains are operated, which are not suitable for rush travel.\n\n",{"type":"===","value":[" By bus "]},"\n",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/donanbus.co.jp\/citybus\/ Dōnan Bus"]}," operates Highway bus (Intercity bus) services.\n",{"type":"*","value":[" \"Highway Pegasus\" (高速ペガサス号) - From ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Sapporo"]]}," to ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Urakawa"]]}," via Monbetsu ward with 7-8 round trips per day. It must be booked."]},{"type":"*","value":[" \"Highway Hidaka\" (高速ひだか号) - From Sapporo to Hidaka ward via Monbetsu ward and Biratori town with a round trip per day."]},{"type":"*","value":[" \"Highway Urakawa\" (高速うらかわ号) - From New Chitose Airport to Urakawa via ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Tomakomai"]]}," and Monbetsu ward with a round trip per day."]},{"type":"*","value":[" \"Express Hidaka\" (特急ひだか号) - From Tomakomai to Hidaka ward via Monbetsu ward and Biratori town with a round trip per day."]},"\nThere is another local bus service, from ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Shimukappu"]]}," to Hidaka ward.\n\n",{"type":"===","value":[" By car "]},"\nHidaka Expwy is through from Tomakomai. The end of  is the Hidaka-Monbetsu IC current, which will extend to the east in the future.\n\nNational Route 235 passes through Monbetsu ward on its way from Tomakomai to Urakawa. National Route 237 runs from ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Furano"]]}," to Monbetsu ward. National Route 274 passes through Hidaka ward on its way from ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Yubari"]]}," to ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Tokachi"]]},".\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get around"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["See"]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["see"],["name=Nibutani Ainu Culture Museum"],["alt=二風谷アイヌ文化博物館"],["url=http:\/\/www.town.biratori.hokkaido.jp\/biratori\/nibutani\/"],["email="],["address=55 Nibutani, Biratori-chō  平取町二風谷55"],["lat=42.63686"],["long=142.15682"],["directions="],["phone=+81 1457 2-2892"],["tollfree="],["fax=+81 1457 2-2828"],["hours=9AM - 5PM"],["price=¥400."],["content=Display of the materials of Ainu culture."]]}]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Do"]},"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["do"],["name=Hidaka international ski area"],["alt= 日高国際スキー場"],["url="],["email="],["address= Tomioka, Hidaka-cho (日高町字富岡)"],["lat= 42.8689"],["long= 142.4496"],["directions="],["phone= +81 1457 6-3667"],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours="],["price="],["content="]]}]},{"type":"[[","value":[["File:Monbetsu spa roten.JPG"],["thumb"],["150px"],["Outdoor bath of Monbetsu Hot Spring"]]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["do"],["name= Monbetsu Hot Spring"],["alt= 門別温泉 とねっこの湯"],["url= http:\/\/www.town.hidaka.hokkaido.jp\/tonekko\/main.html"],["email="],["address= 150-223, Tomihama, Hidaka-cho (日高町字富浜223番地150)"],["lat= 42.4971"],["long= 142.0522"],["directions="],["phone= +81 1456 3-4126"],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours= 10:00AM - 8:30PM"],["price=¥ 500"],["content="]]}]},{